81
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:53,460
Please, help me.

82
00:03:53,460 --> 00:03:54,900
Help me!

83
00:03:55,700 --> 00:03:57,500
Please.

84
00:03:57,500 --> 00:04:00,020
Don't leave me alone.

85
00:04:00,940 --> 00:04:03,140
I'm so miserable.

86
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:04,700
Boss, what do we do?

87
00:04:04,700 --> 00:04:05,980
Of course, we let her go.

88
00:04:05,980 --> 00:04:07,020
What a waste!

89
00:04:07,940 --> 00:04:08,740
A waste?

90
00:04:09,980 --> 00:04:12,580
How about we give her to him as a gift?

91
00:04:12,820 --> 00:04:13,340
Good idea.

92
00:04:13,340 --> 00:04:14,380
Boss, brilliant.

93
00:04:14,380 --> 00:04:14,860
Stop it.

94
00:04:14,860 --> 00:04:15,420
Boss.

95
00:04:15,420 --> 00:04:16,380
I'll deal with you later.

96
00:04:19,900 --> 00:04:21,700
Isn't this rabbit I caught chubby?

97
00:04:21,700 --> 00:04:22,660
It is.

98
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:26,900
Boss.

99
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:29,180
