100
00:04:29,180 --> 00:04:30,820
I caught it in the mountains.

101
00:04:31,020 --> 00:04:32,180
You may catch anything,

102
00:04:32,340 --> 00:04:33,380
but not rabbits.

103
00:04:33,660 --> 00:04:34,300
Set it free.

104
00:04:34,300 --> 00:04:34,900
Then...

105
00:04:35,260 --> 00:04:37,300
What to do if the chief
of the Heifeng Gang comes?

106
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:39,860
It's not proper
to only offer them potatoes, right?

107
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:43,100
I don't eat potatoes.

108
00:04:43,220 --> 00:04:45,380
I'm here to drink good wine
and eat good meat.

109
00:04:45,580 --> 00:04:47,540
If you want to buy me off
with this thing,

110
00:04:47,540 --> 00:04:48,780
that won't work.

111
00:04:49,740 --> 00:04:50,980
What's he doing here?

112
00:04:51,900 --> 00:04:53,020
It must be...

113
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:57,620
Here's a greeting present for you.

114
00:04:57,940 --> 00:04:59,700
A lady from a rich Shengdong family.

115
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:02,420
What do I get in return?

116
00:05:03,700 --> 00:05:04,900
One with huge goals

117
00:05:05,740 --> 00:05:07,220
doesn't indulge in eating and drinking.

118
00:05:08,020 --> 00:05:09,620
If you can be less reckless,

119
00:05:10,460 --> 00:05:11,940
you may achieve great things.

120
00:05:11,940 --> 00:05:13,820
Little Master? It is Little Master.

121
00:05:15,660 --> 00:05:17,220
Why do you care
if I'll achieve anything?

122
00:05:17,660 --> 00:05:20,140
In the Heifeng Gang,
I have achieved many things.

123
00:05:26,460 --> 00:05:27,660
If you can obey me

124
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:29,260
and do the right things,

125
00:05:30,300 --> 00:05:32,220
I promise you'll have wine
and meat every day.

126
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:34,620
I'll also give you three thousand men.

127
00:05:34,860 --> 00:05:35,540
What do you say?

128
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:37,900
Three thousand men?

129
00:05:38,300 --> 00:05:39,340
Don't lie to me.

130
00:05:39,340 --> 00:05:41,060
I always keep my word.

131
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:45,340
It sounds too good to be true, Boss.

132
00:05:47,140 --> 00:05:47,940
We'll do what you ask, Boss.

133
00:05:47,940 --> 00:05:49,540
- We'll count on you from now on.
- Thank you.

134
00:05:49,540 --> 00:05:51,060
- Boss.
- Boss.

135
00:05:52,060 --> 00:05:54,020
But there's a rule when you work for me.

136
00:05:56,100 --> 00:05:58,420
All looted items must be returned.

137
00:05:59,380 --> 00:06:00,700
The so-called greeting gift

138
00:06:01,140 --> 00:06:02,060
