139
00:06:07,780 --> 00:06:08,460
Send it back.

140
00:06:10,460 --> 00:06:11,260
Sure.

141
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:12,860
I know what to do.

142
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:13,780
Good.

143
00:06:14,340 --> 00:06:15,940
Serve the good wine and meat.

144
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:16,780
Great.

145
00:06:17,380 --> 00:06:18,820
Good wine and good meat!

146
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:19,620
Serve the drink.

147
00:06:19,900 --> 00:06:21,540
Go, go. Let's go.

148
00:06:22,300 --> 00:06:23,060
Get more wine.

149
00:06:23,060 --> 00:06:24,020
Okay.

150
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:43,980
I've come all the way here to find you.

151
00:06:44,060 --> 00:06:45,940
Yet you want to send me back?

152
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:48,260
Do you have any idea
how worried I was about you?

153
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:49,380
I worry about you when eating.

154
00:06:49,380 --> 00:06:50,340
I worry about you when sleeping.

155
00:06:50,340 --> 00:06:51,860
When a crow flies above me,

156
00:06:51,860 --> 00:06:53,820
I even want to ask it
to send you a letter.

157
00:06:54,260 --> 00:06:54,940
You...

158
00:06:55,100 --> 00:06:57,300
Yet you want to send me back.

159
00:07:04,660 --> 00:07:05,380
No.

160
00:07:07,420 --> 00:07:08,420
I'll never send you back.

161
00:07:20,060 --> 00:07:21,780
Boss, are we still sending her back?

162
00:07:22,580 --> 00:07:23,780
Didn't you ask us to send her back?

163
00:07:24,780 --> 00:07:26,500
- Yeah. Are we still sending her back?
- Yeah. Are we still sending her back?

164
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:28,500
- Let's send her back.
- Let's send her back.

165
00:07:29,460 --> 00:07:30,260
- Keep her.
- Keep her.

166
00:07:30,260 --> 00:07:31,860
Yeah, that's right.

167
00:07:31,860 --> 00:07:32,740
Send her back or not?

168
00:07:45,260 --> 00:07:46,300
What is this?

169
00:07:47,380 --> 00:07:48,740
The weapons they made themselves

170
00:07:48,740 --> 00:07:49,580
