186
00:08:47,980 --> 00:08:49,180
Should I go out?

187
00:08:49,740 --> 00:08:50,580
It's not like the Eastern Palace.

188
00:08:50,580 --> 00:08:51,700
There are not many rooms here.

189
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:53,540
If you don't allow me to sleep here,

190
00:08:54,980 --> 00:08:56,220
I'll have to sleep outside.

191
00:08:59,260 --> 00:09:02,820
Then you sleep in the bed.

192
00:09:03,060 --> 00:09:04,340
I'll sleep on the floor.

193
00:09:18,420 --> 00:09:20,140
How can I bear
to allow my Crown Princess

194
00:09:21,940 --> 00:09:22,940
to sleep on the floor?

195
00:09:41,060 --> 00:09:42,100
All right. I won't tease you.

196
00:09:42,260 --> 00:09:42,980
Go to bed.

197
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:09,300
Little Master.

198
00:10:12,980 --> 00:10:13,820
Little Master.

199
00:10:16,660 --> 00:10:17,900
Are you asleep?

200
00:10:46,860 --> 00:10:48,020
Are you afraid that I can't sleep

201
00:10:49,780 --> 00:10:50,900
or that I've fallen asleep?

202
00:10:52,460 --> 00:10:53,460
I...

203
00:10:53,460 --> 00:10:55,950
♪It's your mesmerizing glance♪

204
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:59,410
♪Freezing the gentle breeze
of the mundane world♪

205
00:10:59,660 --> 00:11:04,970
♪Your gentle call awakens me
from my unfinished dreams♪

206
00:11:05,550 --> 00:11:08,740
♪It's hard to convey my love for you
when fighting for the homeland♪

207
00:11:09,030 --> 00:11:12,380
♪Our destined encounter♪

208
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:16,390
♪I am meant to accompany you
on this journey♪

209
00:11:23,300 --> 00:11:24,060
Hurry up!

210
00:11:24,060 --> 00:11:24,780
All right.

211
00:11:27,460 --> 00:11:28,060
Do you feel cold?

212
00:11:29,420 --> 00:11:30,100
Yeah.

213
00:11:35,180 --> 00:11:35,620
Are you still cold?

214
00:11:35,620 --> 00:11:36,380
Still cold.

215
00:11:39,220 --> 00:11:40,140
It's not cold now.

216
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:44,820
If only we could stay like this forever.

217
00:11:48,660 --> 00:11:50,060
Despite living a humble life
with simple meals,

218
00:11:51,180 --> 00:11:52,140
with you by my side,

219
00:11:52,580 --> 00:11:53,460
I am happy.

220
00:11:54,140 --> 00:11:54,900
Me too.

221
00:11:55,540 --> 00:11:57,060
As long as you are by my side,

222
00:11:57,060 --> 00:11:58,540
mantou can be

223
00:11:58,540 --> 00:12:00,260
as tasty as a lavish feast.

224
00:12:06,580 --> 00:12:07,700
On my way back,

225
00:12:09,420 --> 00:12:11,500
I saw a lot of displaced people.

226
00:12:14,340 --> 00:12:15,860
They don't even have mantou.

227
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:18,660
I really can't bear it

228
00:12:20,580 --> 00:12:21,420
and I'm unreconciled.

229
00:12:22,100 --> 00:12:23,940
If we don't stop Xingshi
from ruling the country like this,

230
00:12:23,940 --> 00:12:24,860
it'll be destroyed soon.

231
00:12:25,860 --> 00:12:27,020
In my opinion,

232
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:30,260
it doesn't matter whether we call
the country Jixi or Shengdong,

233
00:12:30,740 --> 00:12:33,620
