that the people can live a good life.

234
00:12:35,260 --> 00:12:36,140
Do you really think so?

235
00:12:36,140 --> 00:12:36,940
Of course.

236
00:12:38,260 --> 00:12:40,860
If you want to return to the palace,

237
00:12:40,860 --> 00:12:41,740
I'll support you.

238
00:12:48,460 --> 00:12:49,860
I have a great chance,

239
00:12:50,980 --> 00:12:52,980
