250
00:13:21,180 --> 00:13:22,700
I won't make you suffer.

251
00:13:25,900 --> 00:13:26,900
I believe you.

252
00:13:27,340 --> 00:13:28,740
You won't make me

253
00:13:29,060 --> 00:13:30,860
or the common people suffer.

