258
00:14:06,100 --> 00:14:06,820
Who are you?

259
00:14:07,740 --> 00:14:08,380
Stop.

260
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:11,340
Who are you?

261
00:14:21,340 --> 00:14:22,300
Nangong Yao.

262
00:14:25,460 --> 00:14:26,380
Attack.

263
00:14:38,020 --> 00:14:38,580
Douzi.

264
00:14:38,580 --> 00:14:39,420
You can't go out.

265
00:14:40,340 --> 00:14:42,260
The Crown Prince doesn't let you go
for your good.

266
00:14:42,260 --> 00:14:42,860
Exactly.

267
00:14:42,860 --> 00:14:44,380
No one can guarantee you won't be hurt
by weapons when fighting.

268
00:14:44,380 --> 00:14:46,380
Yeah, well, in the battle,

269
00:14:46,380 --> 00:14:47,380
