From now on,

274
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:52,780
don't mention the word "lose"
in front of me.

275
00:14:52,860 --> 00:14:54,020
If you have to say it,

276
00:14:54,140 --> 00:14:56,220
well, then use "meow" instead.

277
00:14:56,260 --> 00:14:57,020
Did you hear me?

278
00:14:57,020 --> 00:14:57,580
What?

279
00:14:57,620 --> 00:14:58,980
Meow. All right.

280
00:14:59,900 --> 00:15:00,580
Uhh...

281
00:15:00,580 --> 00:15:02,980
Is that carriage at the door for me?

282
00:15:03,300 --> 00:15:04,180
His Highness commanded

283
00:15:04,380 --> 00:15:05,340
that if he lost...

284
00:15:08,020 --> 00:15:09,300
If he meowed,

285
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:12,140
just took the box inside

286
00:15:12,260 --> 00:15:13,700
and that carriage in the back.

287
00:15:14,020 --> 00:15:15,300
It's all for you to escape.

288
00:15:23,100 --> 00:15:24,780
We're going to be rich.

289
00:15:24,780 --> 00:15:25,380
Put it down.

290
00:15:26,380 --> 00:15:27,620
Do you have no shame?

291
00:15:28,980 --> 00:15:31,380
My... My hands.

292
00:15:31,380 --> 00:15:31,940
My hands.

293
00:15:31,940 --> 00:15:32,540
Douzi.

294
00:15:32,540 --> 00:15:33,540
Let him go.

295
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:37,420
I'm going to help Little Master today,

296
00:15:37,420 --> 00:15:38,740
even if I'll die.

297
00:15:38,740 --> 00:15:40,220
Even if both of us will die.

298
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:41,580
Even if I'll die,

299
00:15:41,580 --> 00:15:42,980
I will die with him.

300
00:15:43,020 --> 00:15:45,100
Anyone of you would like to go with me?

301
00:15:45,100 --> 00:15:46,180
Raise your hand.

302
00:15:46,980 --> 00:15:47,620
Me.

303
00:15:49,420 --> 00:15:50,740
I am timid,

304
00:15:51,100 --> 00:15:52,300
but you can count me in.

305
00:15:52,820 --> 00:15:53,420
Que.

306
00:15:53,780 --> 00:15:54,340
Que?

307
00:15:54,340 --> 00:15:54,940
Que!

308
00:15:55,020 --> 00:15:55,780
Coming.

309
00:15:56,820 --> 00:15:58,500
Stop talking.

310
00:15:58,500 --> 00:15:59,340
Let's fight them.

311
00:16:29,060 --> 00:16:29,980
Guys,

312
00:16:30,260 --> 00:16:31,700
this is the Hall of Supreme Harmony.

313
00:16:32,300 --> 00:16:33,940
I thought it was hard to get in.

314
00:16:34,140 --> 00:16:35,580
But it was so easy.

315
00:16:36,020 --> 00:16:36,740
Come on.

316
00:16:37,820 --> 00:16:38,460
Let's go.

317
00:16:50,780 --> 00:16:52,420
- Boss, good job.
- Boss, good job.

318
00:17:05,740 --> 00:17:06,660
Let him go.

319
00:17:06,660 --> 00:17:09,260
I knew something was wrong with Bai Ye.

320
00:17:09,860 --> 00:17:11,660
After that day he went out
of the palace to deliver information,

321
00:17:12,340 --> 00:17:14,260
I found out
when you'd come to the palace

322
00:17:14,580 --> 00:17:16,020
and what you were going to do.

323
00:17:16,620 --> 00:17:18,140
I knew everything

324
00:17:18,380 --> 00:17:19,620
so I was waiting for you

325
00:17:20,100 --> 00:17:21,420
to come and arrest you.

326
00:17:21,660 --> 00:17:22,580
Let him go.

327
00:17:22,660 --> 00:17:23,340
Xingshi,

328
00:17:23,940 --> 00:17:25,980
I was done with the Crown Prince
a long time ago.

329
00:17:26,980 --> 00:17:28,300
Threatening him with me

330
00:17:29,060 --> 00:17:30,380
won't work.

331
00:17:32,140 --> 00:17:32,820
Your Highness,

332
00:17:33,900 --> 00:17:36,620
I destroyed your country
and caused you to be exiled before.

333
00:17:37,580 --> 00:17:38,420
Now

334
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:41,980
I got you surrounded again.

335
00:17:43,260 --> 00:17:44,660
I'm not worth it.

336
00:17:44,900 --> 00:17:46,140
I'm not worth your saving.

337
00:17:49,300 --> 00:17:49,980
Your Highness,

338
00:17:50,700 --> 00:17:52,260
if you put down your weapon now,

339
00:17:54,940 --> 00:17:56,500
it'll only make me feel more guilty.

340
00:17:58,540 --> 00:18:00,340
If it were me pointed by his sword now,

341
00:18:02,540 --> 00:18:04,500
I'm sure you'd do the same thing.

342
00:18:05,780 --> 00:18:06,500
Your Highness.

343
00:18:27,860 --> 00:18:29,180
Get out of the way.

344
00:18:30,780 --> 00:18:32,060
I'm your princess.

345
00:18:32,060 --> 00:18:33,300
Get out of my way.

346
00:18:33,860 --> 00:18:34,900
Step aside.

347
00:18:36,060 --> 00:18:37,220
Step aside.

348
00:18:40,060 --> 00:18:41,380
Step aside.

349
00:18:45,380 --> 00:18:46,100
Walk away.

350
00:18:46,940 --> 00:18:47,700
Step aside.

351
00:18:54,300 --> 00:18:55,060
Stop.

352
00:18:59,700 --> 00:19:00,700
Little Master!

353
00:19:01,620 --> 00:19:02,340
Princess?

354
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:04,740
What are you doing here?

355
00:19:04,860 --> 00:19:06,500
I am affectionate and righteous.

356
00:19:06,540 --> 00:19:08,220
I'll go wherever you go.

357
00:19:10,620 --> 00:19:12,140
You are the Princess of Shengdong.

358
00:19:12,420 --> 00:19:14,740
I can't believe you mingle
with our enemy of Jixi.

359
00:19:14,740 --> 00:19:16,700
I'm only standing
on the side of justice.

360
00:19:18,820 --> 00:19:19,500
Wait.

361
00:19:19,660 --> 00:19:21,340
I'm standing
on the side of justice and my lover.

362
00:19:46,660 --> 00:19:47,940
Protect His Highness.

363
00:20:09,980 --> 00:20:10,780
Still fighting?

364
00:20:11,100 --> 00:20:11,780
No more fighting.

365
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:13,060
You go there.

366
00:20:38,820 --> 00:20:40,820
You, there.

367
00:20:40,820 --> 00:20:41,820
You too.

368
00:20:43,700 --> 00:20:45,100
You idiot.

369
00:20:45,100 --> 00:20:46,060
How dare you touch our Crown Princess!

370
00:20:46,060 --> 00:20:47,100
I'll kill you.

371
00:20:47,140 --> 00:20:48,180
If it weren't for the Princess,

372
00:20:48,180 --> 00:20:49,460
I would have killed you by now.

373
00:20:50,780 --> 00:20:52,340
You can argue.

374
00:20:52,380 --> 00:20:53,900
But no more fighting. You hear me?

375
00:20:55,460 --> 00:20:56,620
No more fighting.

376
00:20:56,940 --> 00:20:57,620
Big Head Yu.

377
00:21:00,100 --> 00:21:01,660
Come on, Second Father, catch this.

378
00:21:03,100 --> 00:21:04,460
Listen to me.

379
00:21:04,460 --> 00:21:05,820
Don't you dare fight!

380
00:21:05,820 --> 00:21:07,740
Otherwise, I'll hit you

381
00:21:07,740 --> 00:21:09,060
with my hammer here.

382
00:21:10,700 --> 00:21:11,340
Third Father.

383
00:21:11,500 --> 00:21:12,100
Take this.

384
00:21:12,220 --> 00:21:12,780
Okay.

385
00:21:13,140 --> 00:21:14,620
You are in charge here.

386
00:21:15,460 --> 00:21:16,580
Don't worry.

387
00:21:25,940 --> 00:21:27,140
Why are they fighting again?

388
00:21:27,140 --> 00:21:28,100
How long has it been?

389
00:21:28,860 --> 00:21:29,540
How's it?

390
00:21:29,540 --> 00:21:30,700
Did Little Master get hurt?

391
00:21:38,220 --> 00:21:39,020
Little Master,

392
00:21:39,020 --> 00:21:40,980
why don't you take a break
and let me do it for you?

393
00:21:45,500 --> 00:21:47,020
Little Master, be careful.

394
00:21:55,660 --> 00:21:57,220
Surrender now,

395
00:21:57,660 --> 00:21:59,260
I can spare your life.

396
00:21:59,500 --> 00:22:01,020
I should be the one to say that.

397
00:23:15,380 --> 00:23:16,260
Mei.

398
00:23:16,540 --> 00:23:17,780
You're awful.

399
00:23:17,780 --> 00:23:19,980
It's all your fault.

400
00:23:20,020 --> 00:23:21,820
Go get the physicians.

401
00:23:22,140 --> 00:23:23,340
Mei Daidai.

402
00:23:28,620 --> 00:23:30,140
This is your fault.

403
00:23:30,220 --> 00:23:31,940
Go get the physicians.

404
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:33,220
Go get the physicians!

405
00:23:33,220 --> 00:23:33,700
Mei...

406
00:23:33,700 --> 00:23:34,220
Go.

407
00:23:34,220 --> 00:23:34,980
Please don't die.

408
00:23:34,980 --> 00:23:35,540
Yes.

409
00:23:37,180 --> 00:23:38,540
Physicians!

410
00:23:40,900 --> 00:23:41,820
Just now

411
00:23:43,940 --> 00:23:46,740
you were standing on the side
of the Crown Prince.

412
00:23:50,060 --> 00:23:50,780
Now

413
00:23:52,380 --> 00:23:54,580
you gave your life for me.

414
00:23:55,620 --> 00:23:56,580
I'm sorry.

415
00:24:00,340 --> 00:24:01,860
I just understood your heart now.

416
00:24:06,020 --> 00:24:07,060
It's my fault.

417
00:24:20,860 --> 00:24:23,380
How could you leave me behind?

418
00:24:30,140 --> 00:24:31,620
Your Highness, are you all right?

419
00:24:31,620 --> 00:24:32,900
Mei,

420
00:24:35,260 --> 00:24:36,740
you can't die.

421
00:25:18,140 --> 00:25:19,580
I hired the best craftsmen

422
00:25:19,580 --> 00:25:21,020
to fix the Moon Spirit Pearl.

423
00:25:21,660 --> 00:25:23,260
Tonight we have the full moon.

424
00:25:23,260 --> 00:25:24,780
I've decided to give it another try.

425
00:25:28,060 --> 00:25:29,700
I'm not going to let you die.

426
00:25:32,100 --> 00:25:34,180
If one of us has to die,

427
00:25:35,420 --> 00:25:37,020
I would switch my body with yours

428
00:25:37,260 --> 00:25:38,420
and exchange my life with your life.

429
00:25:41,900 --> 00:25:42,420
No, no.

430
00:25:42,860 --> 00:25:43,740
You can't do it.

431
00:25:47,260 --> 00:25:48,380
Did you find the Grand Tutor yet?

432
00:25:48,500 --> 00:25:49,140
I'm warning you,

433
00:25:49,180 --> 00:25:50,660
if this works,

434
00:25:50,660 --> 00:25:52,620
you need to ask him to save me at once.

435
00:25:52,740 --> 00:25:54,780
Or I will haunt you as a ghost.

436
00:25:54,780 --> 00:25:56,100
I'll show up in the Grand Tutor's dreams

437
00:25:56,100 --> 00:25:58,140
to remind him
of asking you to recite books.

438
00:25:59,140 --> 00:26:00,140
I see.

439
00:26:08,780 --> 00:26:09,540
Besides,

440
00:26:10,220 --> 00:26:12,380
you can't allow him to suck my blood
with a poisonous worm.

441
00:26:12,380 --> 00:26:13,100
Otherwise, I'll...

442
00:27:00,500 --> 00:27:01,700
Did it really work?

443
00:27:01,780 --> 00:27:02,740
Oh no.

444
00:27:03,100 --> 00:27:04,660
How do I tell this to Yao?

445
00:27:06,540 --> 00:27:07,580
Grand Tutor!

446
00:27:07,740 --> 00:27:08,620
Hurry.

447
00:27:09,540 --> 00:27:11,060
I heard there was someone

448
00:27:11,060 --> 00:27:13,500
who was almost dead.

449
00:27:17,020 --> 00:27:18,260
Why did she faint here?

450
00:27:18,780 --> 00:27:19,900
I don't know.

451
00:27:19,900 --> 00:27:21,420
Save the dying one first.

452
00:27:22,380 --> 00:27:23,260
Step aside.

453
00:27:52,860 --> 00:27:54,460
Too bad it was a little off.

454
00:27:54,460 --> 00:27:56,300
It was so close to the heart.

455
00:27:57,180 --> 00:27:59,620
Any closer to the heart
and she'd be dead.

456
00:28:01,540 --> 00:28:02,260
Don't worry.

457
00:28:06,940 --> 00:28:08,220
My cutie.

458
00:28:09,260 --> 00:28:11,420
This one is big and strong.

459
00:28:15,860 --> 00:28:16,740
She is dying.

460
00:28:16,740 --> 00:28:18,140
You want to suck her blood with this?

461
00:28:19,340 --> 00:28:20,380
Should I save her or not?

462
00:28:20,380 --> 00:28:22,740
You should.

463
00:28:26,460 --> 00:28:27,740
I'll put it here.

464
00:28:42,540 --> 00:28:43,940
Look, look.

465
00:28:56,100 --> 00:28:56,980
That's enough.

466
00:28:56,980 --> 00:28:58,180
All the blood's sucked out.

467
00:28:58,900 --> 00:29:00,180
Do something about it.

468
00:29:00,860 --> 00:29:03,140
If this keeps up, Miss Mei will die.

469
00:29:03,820 --> 00:29:05,340
Do something about it, Grand Tutor.

470
00:29:06,860 --> 00:29:08,260
This really must stop.

471
00:29:13,740 --> 00:29:14,500
Grand Tutor.

472
00:29:22,300 --> 00:29:23,180
Her hand moved.

473
00:29:24,100 --> 00:29:25,060
Her hand.

474
00:29:28,180 --> 00:29:29,100
It worked.

475
00:29:35,740 --> 00:29:37,100
Now you are full.

476
00:29:39,380 --> 00:29:40,780
Good.

477
00:29:43,180 --> 00:29:44,540
Weren't there two worms?

478
00:29:45,060 --> 00:29:46,380
Why is there only one left?

479
00:29:48,660 --> 00:29:49,500
Right.

480
00:29:49,940 --> 00:29:51,060
Where is the other one?

481
00:29:51,820 --> 00:29:53,220
Then look for it.

482
00:29:53,620 --> 00:29:54,140
Look for it.

483
00:29:55,540 --> 00:29:56,660
Where are you looking?

484
00:29:57,220 --> 00:29:58,700
Are you sure it's on her?

485
00:29:58,700 --> 00:30:00,300
If it's not on her, then it's on her.

486
00:30:00,300 --> 00:30:01,420
Look for it.

487
00:30:01,620 --> 00:30:02,340
Not this one, either.

488
00:30:02,340 --> 00:30:02,940
My worm...

489
00:30:03,420 --> 00:30:04,380
Well, then where can I find my worm?

490
00:30:04,460 --> 00:30:05,900
Neither this one nor that one.

491
00:30:05,980 --> 00:30:06,820
Listen,

492
00:30:07,740 --> 00:30:08,860
if you don't find this one,

493
00:30:09,540 --> 00:30:12,180
the other one will come after you.

494
00:30:15,100 --> 00:30:15,620
Look for it.

495
00:30:36,100 --> 00:30:37,860
I can't believe
you still have an appetite.

496
00:30:40,700 --> 00:30:42,940
Knowing the one I love survived,

497
00:30:43,420 --> 00:30:44,460
I'm in a good mood.

498
00:30:45,260 --> 00:30:46,300
Of course, I'll eat more.

499
00:30:47,180 --> 00:30:48,380
Don't you worry about yourself?

500
00:30:49,220 --> 00:30:50,660
I'll die without anything to regret.

501
00:30:51,500 --> 00:30:52,620
For me,

502
00:30:53,020 --> 00:30:54,660
whatever conviction I end up with,

503
00:30:55,500 --> 00:30:57,380
it'll be easier than being the emperor.

504
00:30:58,460 --> 00:30:59,340
You are conscious.

505
00:31:00,940 --> 00:31:01,980
If you could see this through earlier,

506
00:31:03,100 --> 00:31:04,780
you wouldn't have ended up here.

507
00:31:04,780 --> 00:31:06,500
You don't have to worry about me.

508
00:31:07,300 --> 00:31:09,700
Being an emperor, you'll have to
shoulder lots of responsibilities.

509
00:31:10,700 --> 00:31:13,220
The one who works hard in the future

510
00:31:13,940 --> 00:31:14,740
will be you.

511
00:31:30,250 --> 00:31:31,860
[Yong'an Gate]

512
00:31:31,860 --> 00:31:34,180
Nangong Yao ascended the throne
as the Emperor

513
00:31:34,380 --> 00:31:36,460
and changed the country's name
back to Jixi.

514
00:31:37,180 --> 00:31:39,020
Xingshi was exiled to Shengdong

515
00:31:39,620 --> 00:31:42,900
and could never
take one step back in Jixi.

516
00:31:48,380 --> 00:31:49,860
[Grand Chancellor's Residence]
Father, mother.

517
00:31:50,340 --> 00:31:51,660
I'm now bidding my farewell to you.

518
00:31:52,380 --> 00:31:54,940
Why do you have to
give up the glory and wealth

519
00:31:54,940 --> 00:31:56,620
to go to that Xingshi?

520
00:31:57,100 --> 00:31:58,620
He was sent into exile.

521
00:31:58,620 --> 00:32:00,140
What for?

522
00:32:01,500 --> 00:32:02,460
All right.

523
00:32:04,540 --> 00:32:05,380
Stop talking.

524
00:32:05,820 --> 00:32:06,820
Let her go.

525
00:32:07,820 --> 00:32:10,900
At least our sons have jobs
in the imperial court now.

526
00:32:11,220 --> 00:32:11,940
Right?

527
00:32:12,620 --> 00:32:14,100
I didn't expect you

528
00:32:14,100 --> 00:32:15,260
to take care of us

529
00:32:15,260 --> 00:32:17,420
when we grow old.

530
00:32:18,860 --> 00:32:19,540
You can go now.

531
00:32:19,980 --> 00:32:20,740
We'll just forget

532
00:32:21,700 --> 00:32:23,700
we ever had a daughter.

533
00:32:25,020 --> 00:32:25,860
Just go.

534
00:32:28,260 --> 00:32:29,140
Shan.

535
00:32:30,260 --> 00:32:30,900
Father,

536
00:32:31,540 --> 00:32:32,180
mother,

537
00:32:32,780 --> 00:32:35,100
Douzi will take care of you for me.

538
00:32:35,660 --> 00:32:36,540
Shan.

539
00:32:40,100 --> 00:32:41,460
I hate to see you leave.

540
00:32:41,940 --> 00:32:44,740
You dress only in soft yarn.

541
00:32:44,740 --> 00:32:46,220
You sleep with white jade pillows.

542
00:32:46,340 --> 00:32:47,540
Even when you have bitter gourd,

543
00:32:47,540 --> 00:32:49,100
you make it too fancy.

544
00:32:49,580 --> 00:32:50,940
I'm afraid, in Shengdong,

545
00:32:50,940 --> 00:32:52,020
you'll not be used to it.

546
00:32:52,460 --> 00:32:53,260
Don't worry.

547
00:32:53,380 --> 00:32:54,420
I'll get used to it.

548
00:32:56,140 --> 00:32:57,300
I forbid you to get used to it.

549
00:32:58,060 --> 00:32:58,660
Come here.

550
00:33:00,300 --> 00:33:02,140
I've got a wagon full of things for you.

551
00:33:02,580 --> 00:33:04,820
Write to me if you run out of it.

552
00:33:06,500 --> 00:33:08,100
These gold and jewels

553
00:33:08,100 --> 00:33:09,620
should be enough for you for a while.

554
00:33:11,060 --> 00:33:13,220
If you run out of things on the road,

555
00:33:13,220 --> 00:33:14,260
just sell them.

556
00:33:14,380 --> 00:33:15,420
They'll get you some money.

557
00:33:17,700 --> 00:33:18,300
All right.

558
00:33:18,540 --> 00:33:19,780
Just take these for now.

559
00:33:19,980 --> 00:33:21,740
If you bring too much,
people might rob you.

560
00:33:23,100 --> 00:33:25,900
I heard it from Mrs. Mei
that the bitter gourd you have

561
00:33:25,900 --> 00:33:27,540
takes an hour to carve.

562
